report
Class MessageDeliveryReport

java.lang.Object
  report.Report
      report.MessageDeliveryReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
MessageListener
public class MessageDeliveryReport
extends Report
implements MessageListener

Report for of amount of messages delivered vs. time. A new report line is created every time when either a message is created or delivered. Messages created during the warm up period are ignored. For output syntax, see HEADER.
